{"title":"秋播（诗二首）","authors":["粟鹤皋"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":9,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋播（诗二首）\t湖南通道侗族自治县双江公社   粟鹤皋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月湖南遍地春，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"薯苗嫩绿晚禾青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋播红旗坡顶笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阵阵山歌绕白云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小伙子吆牛前边走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们含笑紧相跟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种啊播种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕耘啊耕耘……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山歌声声平地起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员都是唱歌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人大哥来伴奏——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播种机是架大钢琴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶播"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八月丹桂香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月菊花黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天高气爽雁南飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋播好时光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天烟遮日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚火满岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧垦再施肥万担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员播种忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早撒一把籽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多收千箩粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八九两月金不换，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫待寒霜降！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}